                    <p><strong>Est. ROI:</strong> ~70.31%</p>
                    <p><strong>Analysis:</strong> An expensive, discontinued case. Its high price is due to scarcity. The ROI remains respectable because it contains classic, highly sought-after knife finishes (Case Hardened, Slaughter) for foundational knives like the Karambit and M9 Bayonet.</p>
                     <p><strong>Chase Item:</strong> <span class="chase-item">Karambit | Case Hardened</span></p>
