                    <p><strong>Est. ROI:</strong> ~55-60%</p>
                    <p><strong>Analysis:</strong> A very cheap and widely available case. While its overall ROI is lower, its value comes from containing popular skins like the AK-47 | Asiimov and AWP | Neo-Noir at a low entry cost. Excellent for acquiring trade-up fodder.</p>
                    <p><strong>Chase Item:</strong> <span class="chase-item">Talon Knife</span></p>
